717
00:48:56,561 --> 00:48:57,770
Boleh kudengar lagi?

718
00:48:58,354 --> 00:49:00,106
<i>Silakan masuk, Pak Jeong.</i>

719
00:49:00,189 --> 00:49:01,524
Sebentar.

720
00:49:05,027 --> 00:49:08,531
<i>Kenapa kau ke Pabrik Beton Songju semalam?</i>

