00:49:08,906 --> 00:49:10,616
<i>Aku tanda tangan kontrak.</i>

722
00:49:12,410 --> 00:49:14,870
<i>Pak Jeong Sang-hun...</i>

723
00:49:14,954 --> 00:49:15,871
Ulangi bagian itu.

724
00:49:16,080 --> 00:49:18,082
<i>- Pak Jeong Sang-hun...
- Silakan masuk, Pak Jeong.</i>

725
00:49:18,165 --> 00:49:20,126
<i>belum pernah menangani proyek macam ini.</i>

726
00:49:21,502 --> 00:49:23,629
