770
00:51:52,361 --> 00:51:54,155
Ibunya sudah tiada.

771
00:51:56,699 --> 00:51:58,409
Ibu, In Yeong-mi.

772
00:51:58,617 --> 00:51:59,994
Tempat lahir...

773
00:52:00,453 --> 00:52:01,412
Bukan Gangneung.

774
00:52:02,079 --> 00:52:04,790
Tak ada koneksi.

775
00:52:06,542 --> 00:52:08,294
Aku tak melihat kaitan.

776
00:52:08,377 --> 00:52:09,628
CATATAN

777
00:52:09,712 --> 00:52:13,132
Sejak 1994 hingga 2004,

778
00:52:13,215 --> 00:52:14,759
ibunya ada di Yanggye...

779
00:52:15,468 --> 00:52:16,969
"Rumah Sakit Jiwa Yanggye"?

780
00:52:17,052 --> 00:52:18,804
GANGNEUNG

781
00:52:19,472 --> 00:52:21,974
Yanggye-myeon, Gangneung.

782
00:52:22,057 --> 00:52:23,851
RUMAH SAKIT JIWA YANGGYE

783
00:52:23,934 --> 00:52:25,227
Rumah Sakit Jiwa Yanggye.

784
00:52:25,728 --> 00:52:29,064
Baiklah. In Dong-gu terakhir kali terlihat
dalam rekaman di Yanggye-myeon,

785
00:52:29,148 --> 00:52:31,817
dan ibunya pernah masuk
Rumah Sakit Jiwa Yanggye.

786
00:52:31,901 --> 00:52:35,321
Berarti In Dong-gu mengenal
daerah Yanggye-myeon.

787
00:52:35,905 --> 00:52:38,699
Jadi, bisa diasumsikan
dia membawa Jeong Sang-hun

788
00:52:39,492 --> 00:52:43,120
ke Rumah Sakit Jiwa Yanggye.

789
00:52:43,913 --> 00:52:44,914
Benar?

790
00:52:47,666 --> 00:52:48,709
Apa terlalu berlebihan?

791
00:52:54,006 --> 00:52:56,634
<i>Aku ragu itu relevan,</i>

792
00:52:56,717 --> 00:52:58,636
<i>tapi sepertinya dia memang punya koneksi</i>

793
00:52:59,220 --> 00:53:00,846
dengan rumah sakit jiwa itu.

794
00:53:01,138 --> 00:53:02,848
Ada catatan yang menunjukkan

795
00:53:02,932 --> 00:53:06,811
