di Rumah Sakit Jiwa Yanggye.

796
00:53:07,394 --> 00:53:08,896
RUMAH SAKIT JIWA YANGGYE

797
00:53:08,979 --> 00:53:12,066
Aku ragu Jeong Sang-hun ada di sini.

798
00:53:13,275 --> 00:53:14,693
Jika dia sungguh ada di sini,

799
00:53:14,777 --> 00:53:16,737
